description: Under normal circumstances, the fund will invest at least 80% of its net assets (plus the amount of any borrowings for investment purposes) in emerging markets bonds with an average life of 1-10 years denominated in U.S. dollars, either directly or indirectly (e.g., through derivatives). It is non-diversified.
name: BondBloxx JP Morgan USD Emerging Markets 1-10 Year Bond ETF
